    .innertube
      h1(style="color: var(--accent-complement-dark);") Main Objective
      h2 Date
      ul
        li Start: 2024/03/15
        li End: 2024/03/17
      h2 Author:
      ul
        li A93294
        li Pedro Miguel Rodrigues Gomes
      h2 Summary
      ol
        li Data Analysis and Database Creation
          ul
            li Analyze the provided data about music composers and create a suitable dataset to be used with JSON-SERVER.
        li Web Query Service
          ul
            li Use CSS and JavaScript to create a webpage that allows querying composers and musical periods.
            li Develop a web service that responds to HTTP GET requests on the following routes:
              ul
                li 
                  span.code /compositores
                  | -> A listing of all composers.
                li 
                  span.code /compositores/{id}
                  | -> Details about a specific composer.
                li 
                  span.code /compositores?periodo={periodo}
                  | -> A list of composers from a specific period.
                li 
                  span.code /periodos
                  | -> A list of all musical periods present in the dataset.
                li 
                  span.code /periodos/{id}
                  | -> Details about a specific musical period.
        li CRUD Operations
          ul
            li Implement CRUD (Create, Read, Update, Delete) operations for:
              ul
                li 
                  span.code /edit/compositores/{id}
                  | -> To edit composers.
                li 
                  span.code /edit/periodos/{id}
                  | -> To edit musical periods.
                li 
                  span.code /add/compositores
                  | -> To add composers.
                li 
                  span.code /add/periodos
                  | -> To add musical periods.
                li 
                  span.code /delete/compositores
                  | -> To remove composers.
                li 
                  span.code /delete/periodos
                  | -> To remove musical periods.
